   "source": [
    "# k-Armed Bandit\n",
    "\n",
    "- The *value* is the *expected reward*\n",
    "  $$\n",
    "  \\begin{align*}\n",
    "  q_\\star(a) \\doteq& \\textbf{E}[R_t|A_t=a]\\quad\\forall a\\in\\{1,\\cdots,k\\}\\\\\n",
    "  =& \\sum_r{p(r|a)r}\n",
    "  \\end{align*}\n",
    "  $$\n",
    "- the goal is to *maximize* the *expected reward*\n",
    "  $$\n",
    "  \\underset{a}{\\mathrm{argmax}}\\ q_\\star(a)\n",
    "  $$"
   ]
